<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Support — Doorstep</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #faf8f5;
      color: #2a1a0e;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    header {
      background: #2B1A0E;
      padding: 40px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header h1 { color: #C4956A; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    header p  { color: #9A6A40; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 6px; }
    main {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 48px auto;
      padding: 0 24px 80px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2B1A0E;
      margin: 40px 0 12px;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #e8d8c4;
    }
    p  { margin-bottom: 14px; color: #3a2510; }
    ul { margin: 0 0 14px 20px; }
    li { margin-bottom: 8px; color: #3a2510; }
    a  { color: #C4956A; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .contact-card {
      background: #fff8f0;
      border: 1.5px solid #e8d0b0;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 28px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .contact-card p { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .contact-card a {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #C4956A;
    }
    .contact-card .note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9A6A40;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .faq-item { margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .faq-item h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2B1A0E;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 24px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9A6A40;
      border-top: 1px solid #e8d8c4;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Doorstep</h1>
  <p>Support</p>
</header>

<main>

  <p>
    Need help with Doorstep? We're here for you. Reach out via email and we'll get back
    to you as soon as possible.
  </p>

  <div class="contact-card">
    <p>Email us at</p>
    <a href="mailto:support@doorstep.app">support@doorstep.app</a>
    <p class="note">We aim to respond within 1–2 business days.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>How do I delete my account?</h3>
    <p>
      Open the App → Settings → scroll to the bottom → tap <strong>Delete account</strong>.
      Your profile, photos, and messages will be permanently removed within 30 days.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>How do I cancel my subscription?</h3>
    <p>
      Subscriptions are managed by Apple. Go to your iPhone's <strong>Settings → Apple ID →
      Subscriptions</strong>, find Doorstep, and tap Cancel. Your access continues until the
      end of the current billing period.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Can I get a refund?</h3>
    <p>
      Monthly subscriptions can be cancelled any time. Annual subscriptions are non-refundable.
      For billing disputes, contact Apple Support directly as all payments are processed by Apple.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>I can't log in to my account</h3>
    <p>
      Tap <strong>Forgot password</strong> on the login screen to reset via email. If you're
      still having trouble, email us at <a href="mailto:support@doorstep.app">support@doorstep.app</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>How do I report another user?</h3>
    <p>
      Open the conversation or profile → tap the <strong>⋯ menu</strong> → tap
      <strong>Report</strong>. We review all reports and take action where appropriate.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>My messages aren't sending</h3>
    <p>
      Check your internet connection and try again. If the problem persists, close and reopen
      the App. Messages in Doorstep are end-to-end encrypted — if encryption keys are missing,
      signing out and back in will regenerate them.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>I'm not seeing any profiles near me</h3>
    <p>
      Make sure your suburb is set correctly in your profile (Settings → Edit Profile). Doorstep
      matches within your suburb — if your area has few users you may see a limited feed while
      the community grows.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>How do I update my suburb?</h3>
    <p>
      Go to your Profile tab → Edit → update your suburb. Note that your suburb is locked after
      initial setup to preserve neighbourhood integrity. Email us if you've genuinely moved.
    </p>
  </div>

</main>

<footer>
  &copy; 2026 Doorstep. All rights reserved. &nbsp;·&nbsp;
  <a href="privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
  <a href="terms">Terms of Service</a>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
